{"word":"ἀποδυτέος","slug":"ἀποδυτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποδυτέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <el>ἀποδύω.</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>one must strip</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἀπ. ταῖς γυναιξίν</el> <i>they must strip off their clothes</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}